{"tid":1632553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［和 理 非 全 面 進 場］","createTime":"2019-10-06T18:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T18:57:33.000Z","uid":310784,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"875b57d20f985188a32c1adfbec4b001be4ffceb","tid":1632553,"uid":310784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:33:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">P牌仔第一次開Po 細細力屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n勇武手足辛苦晒你地 喺時候和理非進場<br />\n（當然唔反對黑裝修 紅裝飾 藍罷買 黃爆買原則 核爆不割）<br />\n（隨時遍地開花 hit and run 等班狗出嚟撲空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n認真<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> 文宣跟不上</span> </span></strong>加上<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非活動太少 關注度低</span></strong></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">目的：</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">吸引外媒關注</span> 一家大細都可以參與</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">傳遞訊息：是你教我們和平是沒有用</span></span><br />\n <span style=\"font-size: large;\">經過一輪和理非活動 我相信政府係唔會理 所以之後就<span style=\"color: blue;\">名正言順可以升級</span> 同時亦要向外媒傳遞到訊息</span><br />\n<br />\n建議活動如下:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.大型摺紙鶴活動</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2.黃店爆買日</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3.連儂牆狂痴日</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4.超長人鏈</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5.嘉年華式晚會</span><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多相信其他post都有相關建議 呢啲行動絕對唔係想膠化 和理非不割同時 勇武可否都不割？以上活動希望<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家蒙面 拎住各類文宣進行</span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同意請幫手推</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<spa